data.description: **Motivated Sellers and willing to give up to $10,000 towards buyers closing costs, pre-paids, or buy down rate with acceptable offer!*** Welcome to this listing for a stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bath home with a mother-in-law suite and an open floor plan. Situated on over half an acre of land, this property offers privacy and space without the constraints of an HOA. Step inside and be greeted by the elegance of granite countertops throughout the house, adding a touch of luxury to your everyday life. The home has been recently painted and features new carpet in the bedrooms, ensuring a fresh and comfortable living experience. The main living area boasts beautiful tile flooring, providing both durability and style. This house is located in the highly sought-after Spanish Fort school district, ensuring access to excellent education for your family. One of the standout features of this property is the huge fully fenced-in backyard, offering a safe and expansive space for outdoor activities. Additionally, the extended back patio with a fire pit creates the perfect setting for entertaining guests or enjoying cozy evenings under the stars. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional home that combines functionality, style, and a prime location. Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm and convenience this property has to offer.
